 "description": "A name stretched to cover all great fierce birds — though the Roc of legend preys on elephants, so the listed figures are for the small kind: double or treble them for the largest. Rocs nest in the most inaccessible peaks; in the lair there is a 50% chance of 1-6 young (eggs, chicks, fledglings), which can be tamed as steeds. Adults with young in the nest are always hostile; otherwise hostile only to Chaos and Neutrality, ignoring (80%) or befriending (20%) Lawful characters who keep a respectful distance.",
